OL,3,CMPs write to M&S and Co-op as ITV News
OL,4,Clearns new details of cyberattack
OL,6,FThe chair of the Business and Trade
OL,7,FSelect Committee is writing to the
OL,8,Fbosses of Marks and Spencer and The Co-
OL,9,Fop, to express concern about
OL,10,Fcyberattacks faced by both retailers.
OL,12,FIt comes as ITV News has learnt the
OL,13,Fhacking has disrupted loyalty cards,
OL,14,Fhandheld scanners and apps used to
OL,15,Freport security incidents in M&S
OL,16,Fstores.
OL,18,FMPs are seeking reassurance that the
OL,19,Fcompanies are managing the incidents
OL,20,Feffectively, and getting adequate
OL,21,Fsupport from GCHQ and other agencies.
