OL,6,FThe parliamentary committee also wants
OL,7,Fclarity on whether IT systems across
OL,8,Fthe UK retail sector are sufficiently
OL,9,Frobust, and whether ransomeware hacks
OL,10,Fare becoming more frequent and
OL,11,Fsuccessful.
OL,13,FAt M&S, online and app orders are down
OL,14,Ffor a seventh consecutive day.
OL,16,FITV News understands that its stores
OL,17,Fare still facing these issues:
